<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Semitexa — Hello</title>
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        :root {
            --bg:        #0d0f14;
            --surface:   #13161d;
            --border:    #1e2330;
            --accent:    #6366f1;
            --accent-hi: #818cf8;
            --green:     #22c55e;
            --text:      #e2e8f0;
            --muted:     #64748b;
            --radius:    14px;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            padding: 3rem 3.5rem;
            max-width: 560px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
        }

        .logo {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .55rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        .logo-icon {
            width: 38px;
            height: 38px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-hi));
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
        }

        .logo-text {
            font-size: 1.35rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -.3px;
            color: var(--text);
        }

        .logo-text span { color: var(--accent-hi); }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.6rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -.5px;
            line-height: 1.15;
            margin-bottom: .75rem;
        }

        h1 em {
            font-style: normal;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-hi), #a78bfa);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: .95rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        .badges {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: .55rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .4rem;
            background: var(--bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: .3rem .85rem;
            font-size: .78rem;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
        }

        .badge .dot {
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--green);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            margin: 0 0 2rem;
        }

        .steps {
            text-align: left;
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: .75rem;
        }

        .steps li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: .75rem;
            font-size: .875rem;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .steps li .num {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            width: 22px;
            height: 22px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--border);
            color: var(--accent-hi);
            font-size: .7rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 1px;
        }

        .steps li code {
            font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
            font-size: .8rem;
            color: var(--text);
            background: var(--bg);
            padding: .15rem .4rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 2.5rem;
            font-size: .75rem;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        .footer a {
            color: var(--accent-hi);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">

        <div class="logo">
            <div class="logo-icon">⬡</div>
            <div class="logo-text">Semi<span>texa</span></div>
        </div>

        <h1>Hello,<br><em>World!</em></h1>

        <p class="subtitle">
            Your Semitexa project is up and running.<br>
            This page is rendered by a <strong>Payload → Handler → Resource → Twig</strong> pipeline.
        </p>

        <div class="badges">
            <span class="badge"><span class="dot"></span>PHP {{ php_version }}</span>
            <span class="badge"><span class="dot"></span>Swoole {{ swoole_version }}</span>
            <span class="badge"><span class="dot"></span>Twig ready</span>
        </div>

        <hr class="divider">

        <ul class="steps">
            <li>
                <span class="num">1</span>
                <span>Run migrations: <code>./bin/semitexa db:migrate</code></span>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="num">2</span>
                <span>Add a local domain: <code>./bin/semitexa dns:add myapp.test</code></span>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span class="num">3</span>
                <span>Create your first module inside <code>src/modules/</code></span>
            </li>
        </ul>

        <p class="footer">
            <a href="https://semitexa.dev/docs" target="_blank">Documentation</a> ·
            Semitexa Ultimate
        </p>

    </div>
</body>
</html>
